  "stem": "<p>The exponential function <em>g</em> is defined by <em>g</em>(<em>x</em>) = 11&middot;<em>a</em><sup><em>x</em></sup>, where <em>a</em> is a positive constant. If <em>g</em>(2) = 1,331, what is the value of <em>g</em>(3)?</p>",
  "answerOptions": [],
