  ],
  "rationale": "<p>From <em>g</em>(2) = 11&middot;<em>a</em><sup>2</sup> = 1,331, dividing both sides by 11 gives <em>a</em><sup>2</sup> = 121, so <em>a</em> = 11 (since <em>a</em> &gt; 0). Then <em>g</em>(3) = 11&middot;11<sup>3</sup> = 11&middot;1,331 = 14,641.</p>",
